headline: Countdown to Best Buy (BBY) Q3 Earnings: Wall Street Forecasts for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Best Buy (BBY), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended October 2025.
